  26:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****     [..]
  27:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       After reset the device is running from Multiple Speed Internal oscillator
  28:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (4 MHz) with Flash 0 wait state. Flash prefetch buffer, D-Cache
  29:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       and I-Cache are disabled, and all peripherals are off except internal
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccQQjroF.s 			page 2


  30:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       SRAM, Flash and JTAG.
  31:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c **** 
  32:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) There is no prescaler on High speed (AHBs) and Low speed (APBs) busses:
  33:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****           all peripherals mapped on these busses are running at MSI speed.
  34:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) The clock for all peripherals is switched off, except the SRAM and FLASH.
  35:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) All GPIOs are in analog mode, except the JTAG pins which
  36:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****           are assigned to be used for debug purpose.
  37:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c **** 
  38:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****     [..]
  39:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       Once the device started from reset, the user application has to:
  40:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) Configure the clock source to be used to drive the System clock
  41:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****           (if the application needs higher frequency/performance)
  42:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) Configure the System clock frequency and Flash settings
  43:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) Configure the AHB and APB busses prescalers
  44:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) Enable the clock for the peripheral(s) to be used
  45:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****       (+) Configure the clock source(s) for peripherals which clocks are not
  46:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc.c ****           derived from the System clock (SAIx, SYSTICK, RTC, ADC, USB OTG FS/USB FS/SDMMC1/RNG)
